{"tid":1738521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司馬昭之心, 手足可否忍忍?","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T04:09:16.000Z","uid":281242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3061fc72544a660cd580c39bb2e8b42242ade905","tid":1738521,"uid":281242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"何妖琴晚又衝出黎叫取消區選, 畢竟佢做咁大台戲都係想咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時取消左區選, 沿用建制派, 仲撚大擭! 無限延續建制搞衰香港, 又可能推多幾個緊急法措施出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日大家可唔可以忍一忍到選舉結束後再為犧牲左o既手足報仇/ 搞大型行動?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">君子報仇,十年未晚, 況且區選失利對建制打撃好大! 要佢地血債票償!!! 唔好浪費左勇武用血換黎o既民意!!!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然Mon po建制/ 狗無處不在, 但我地呢幾日要建制派信自己仲有機會贏。 就算佢地搵人搞事, 我地都要忍, 唔好出動/ 報仇, 就等佢地自暴其短!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人眼睛係雪亮, 知道一切都係建制詭計。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求,缺一不可! <br />\n<br />\n清算黑警,獨立調查!</span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"2c6f3ccc84291ea63fe02c2fe2a1da287219d973","tid":1738521,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:22:11.000Z","msg":"[黃色經濟圈]你買我就代你捐一半<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738473</a>"},{"pid":"aae92005698b660fd06c262845e60bf4b42033b9","tid":1738521,"uid":281242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzASBZg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzASBZg.png&h=024989a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c08e6aae6afcddfd83db3ee08b4e58107f3aa5b7","tid":1738521,"uid":281242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"黎明行動後，減少勇武行動，直至點票後！"},{"pid":"464dfa694c43ba7015ea26f6e2b47f1f56cb8edb","tid":1